text:
I write a weekly newsletter and one of the segments is builders weekly, where I outline three cool stories, tools, strategies, etc. that will help the builder community build better products.

This week I wrote about... 1. Google’s launching of a ChatGPT competitor 2. Microsoft’s strategy masterclass 3. A framework I’ve been thinking about for building with AI

Each week I write a weekly builders weekly article plus an essay on strategies for building products that users love. I'd love if you check it out!

You can read my latest newsletter here: https://www.bentherebuildingthat.com/p/builders-weekly-week-of-2623.
